          "id": "new-service-key-mismatch",
          "description": "新增 Google 服務時，WaitRate/ClientOptions 的 service key 必須與 auth/scopes.go ServiceScopes map key 和 ratelimiter.go defaultRates map key 完全一致",
          "severity": "P1",
          "tags": ["go", "api", "auth", "ratelimiter"],
          "source": "GA4 & Google Search Console 整合 (2026-03)"
        },
